data.text: In a “very special touch” after their #royalwedding dinner, Harry and Meghan’s guests were served wine gums made with the 1984 Taylor’s Port served at Prince Harry’s christening. All the details of the Duke and Duchess of Sussex’s sumptuous #royalwedding party @thesundaytimes

Harry and Meghan’s #royalwedding  menu featured “exquisite” local and seasonal food sourced from all corners of the UK, Californian wine chosen by Meghan, roast chicken in a nod to their engagement dinner and strawberries from Sandringham #harryandmeghan
